I was just trying to explain how agreement got started in the first place.  It was not an attempt to monopolize a spawn, start a list a mile long, or form some sort of Ragefire club.  It was an attempt to make a crappy camp bearable and help clerics who are not in uber guilds have a shot at their epics.  Agreement worked because people gave it a chance and were willing to help one another even if it meant waiting.  <br>
